<p class="lead">Think back through this week's message. What really stuck out?</p>

<h3 id="we-will-statements"><em>We Will</em> Statements</h3>

<p>We will be an intensely <strong>devoted</strong> church.
<a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/act.2.42-43.niv">Acts 2:42-43</a><br />
We will be an irrationally <strong>generous</strong> church.
<a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/act.2.44-45.niv">Acts 2:44-45</a> <a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/act.4.33-34.niv">Acts 4:33-34</a><br />
We will unapologetically share the love of <strong>Jesus</strong>.
<a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/act.2.47.niv">Acts 2:47</a></p>

<h3 id="moving-forward">Moving Forward</h3>

<p>We will remain radically <strong>devoted</strong> to Jesus and to one another.<br />
We will continue to launch new <strong>churches</strong> in cities across the nation and beyond.<br />
We will always leverage and redeem technology to spread the <strong>gospel</strong>.<br />
We will lead people to become fully devoted followers of <strong>Christ</strong>.</p>

