<h2 id="discussion-questions">Discussion Questions</h2>
<p class="lead">Start talking. Find a conversation starter for your group.</p>

<ul>
  <li>What first drew you to Life.Church? Share your story of how you came to be a part of our church.</li>
  <li>How has our church changed since your first experience?</li>
</ul>

